            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> et perpetu<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> sec<lb break="no" n="2"/>uritati Aeliae Vita<lb break="no" n="3"/>lin<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> coniugi <lb n="4"/>inconparabili <lb n="5"/>qu<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> vixit anno<lb break="no" n="6"/>s XXXIII menses V di<lb break="no" n="7"/>es XVIIII Suriacus S<lb break="no" n="8"/>ecu<surplus>i</surplus>ndinus <expan><abbr>dec</abbr><ex>urio</ex></expan> <lb n="9"/><expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>unicipii</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex cert="low">ogetianae</ex></expan> quatt<expan><ex>u</ex><abbr>orviru</abbr></expan><lb break="no" n="10"/>s <note>sic</note> maritus <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>aciendum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>uravit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Oberhalb des Inschriftfeldes Fries mit Opferszene; darüber die Büsten einer Frau, zweier Männer und dreier Mädchen; unterhalb des Inschriftfeldes Hund, der einen Hasen jagt. Z. 1: Die Buchstaben D und M flankieren den Opferfries.</p>
            </div>
